arch_ima_add_kexec_buffer \- do arch-specific steps to add the IMA buffer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" arch_ima_add_kexec_buffer
.BI "(struct kimage *image "  ","
.BI "unsigned long load_addr "  ","
.BI "size_t size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "image" 12
-- undescribed --
